# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:23
translate portuguese tammy5_8fc5eaa3:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. I was hoping that you would show up today."
    tm "Ei, [pcname]. Estava à espera que aparecesses hoje."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:24
translate portuguese tammy5_0a01ae52:

    # tm "I have a favor to ask you."
    tm "Tenho um favor para te pedir."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:25
translate portuguese tammy5_1c87ad9d:

    # tm "If you have time this week, could you put in a little extra hours and help me train?"
    tm "Se tiveres tempo esta semana, podes dedicar umas horas extra e ajudar-me a treinar?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:26
translate portuguese tammy5_2a86d305:

    # tm "I have a fight one week from today and I feel like I need some extra sparring to get into the right rhythm and mindset, you know?"
    tm "Tenho um combate daqui a uma semana e sinto que preciso de algum sparring extra para entrar no ritmo e na mentalidade certos, percebes?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:27
translate portuguese tammy5_6290e18b:

    # tm "I even took evenings off from Java Lava, so I can spend more time up here."
    tm "Até tirei as noites de folga do Java Lava, para poder passar mais tempo aqui."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:28
translate portuguese tammy5_73b1ac92:

    # tm "You good with helping me spar?"
    tm "Tens disponibilidade para me ajudar no treino?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:32
translate portuguese tammy5_4f9b80dd:

    # tm "That's what I like to hear!"
    tm "É isso que eu gosto de ouvir!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:33
translate portuguese tammy5_2425bb2b:

    # tm "Now get your fine ass up in that ring so I can kick it."
    tm "Agora mete o teu belo rabo no ringue para eu lhe dar uns pontapés."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:36
translate portuguese tammy5_0fc31211:

    # tm "Great, let's get started then."
    tm "Ótimo, vamos começar então."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:39
translate portuguese tammy5_669580a7:

    # tm "I mean, yeah. It is a lot of work."
    tm "Quer dizer, sim. Dá muito trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:40
translate portuguese tammy5_265faf02:

    # tm "That's kind of the point though. That's why they call it \"working\" out."
    tm "Mas é essa a ideia. É por isso que se chama «treinar»."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:41
translate portuguese tammy5_1135a251:

    # tm "Anyway, if you're not into it, that's fine. I'll be here though if you want to help."
    tm "De qualquer forma, se não te apetece, tudo bem. Mas estarei aqui se quiseres ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:48
translate portuguese tammyspar0_90680151:

    # "We get into the ring and train hard for three hours straight."
    "Entramos no ringue e treinamos intensamente durante três horas seguidas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:49
translate portuguese tammyspar0_832dc317:

    # "We practice different positions, practice stand up fighting and movements."
    "Praticamos diferentes posições, lutamos em pé e movimentos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:52
translate portuguese tammyspar0_4d620108:

    # "Until finally, we stop and collapse onto the mat in exhaustion."
    "Até que, finalmente, paramos e caímos exaustos no tapete."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:53
translate portuguese tammyspar0_535745d5:

    # tm "I think that's enough for now."
    tm "Acho que por agora chega."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:54
translate portuguese tammyspar0_cb9c08ec:

    # pc "Yeah, I don't know how many more punches I could take."
    pc "Sim, não sei quantos socos mais conseguiria aguentar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:55
translate portuguese tammyspar0_67943849:

    # tm "Aw, you're fine."
    tm "Ah, estás bem."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:56
translate portuguese tammyspar0_22fdacf8:

    # tm "Thanks for sparring with me though. I felt like it really helped."
    tm "Mas obrigado por treinar comigo. Senti que ajudou mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:57
translate portuguese tammyspar0_0e1da4af:

    # pc "You think you're ready?"
    pc "Achas que estás pronto?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:58
translate portuguese tammyspar0_e746934f:

    # tm "No, not at all. I need a couple more sessions like this."
    tm "Não, de todo. Preciso de mais algumas sessões como esta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:59
translate portuguese tammyspar0_62a75dd2:

    # tm "Think you could come back sometime during the week to spar more? I'll be here in the evening."
    tm "Achas que podes voltar durante a semana para treinar mais? Estarei aqui à noite."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:60
translate portuguese tammyspar0_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:61
translate portuguese tammyspar0_56e3b38a:

    # tm "Also, I'd love to have you in my corner during the fight."
    tm "Além disso, adorava ter-te no meu canto durante o combate."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:62
translate portuguese tammyspar0_d48d741a:

    # pc "I could do that."
    pc "Posso fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:63
translate portuguese tammyspar0_2c10d237:

    # tm "You're kind of good at this stuff you know. You could fight too if you wanted."
    tm "És bastante bom nisto, sabias? Também podias lutar, se quisesses."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:64
translate portuguese tammyspar0_97747303:

    # pc "I'm more of a lover."
    pc "Sou mais do tipo romântico."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:65
translate portuguese tammyspar0_7c210bb3:

    # tm "Oh is that right?"
    tm "Ah, é mesmo?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:66
translate portuguese tammyspar0_1fcc5232:

    # tm "Well, you better hit the showers, lover-boy."
    tm "Bem, é melhor ires para o duche, rapaz romântico."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:67
translate portuguese tammyspar0_efb5c0de:

    # tm "I'm going to clean up and head home. I'm so tired."
    tm "Vou dar uma limpeza e ir para casa. Estou tão cansada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:68
translate portuguese tammyspar0_f91621b1:

    # tm "Thanks again. It was fun."
    tm "Mais uma vez, obrigada. Foi divertido."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:71
translate portuguese tammyspar0_8dc2f452:

    # "She grabs her things and heads to the ladies' showers, while I head to the men's showers."
    "Ela pega nas suas coisas e dirige-se para os duches das mulheres, enquanto eu vou para os dos homens."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:72
translate portuguese tammyspar0_7d804453:

    # "By the time I'm done, she's already gone."
    "Quando termino, ela já se foi embora."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:73
translate portuguese tammyspar0_37a6f478:

    # "It was a fun sparring session though. I'll have to come back and help her spar more before her fight."
    "Mas foi uma sessão de sparring divertida. Vou ter de voltar para a ajudar a treinar mais antes do combate dela."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:79
translate portuguese tammyspar0_cc85c375:

    # "Now I need to hurry and get to school."
    "Agora tenho de me apressar e ir para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:87
translate portuguese tammyspar0_08c4d45a:

    # tm "Did you change your mind? Going to help me train?"
    tm "Mudaste de ideias? Vais ajudar-me a treinar?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:90
translate portuguese tammyspar0_72f2c360:

    # tm "I'm glad. Alright, get in the ring so I can beat you up."
    tm "Ainda bem. Muito bem, entra no ringue para eu te dar uma sova."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:94
translate portuguese tammyspar0_8399f090:

    # tm "Then why are you bothering me? I have to train."
    tm "Então porque é que me estás a incomodar? Tenho de treinar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:103
translate portuguese tammyspar1_6f0ed0c2:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. Ready to help me train?"
    tm "Ei, [pcname]. Pronto para me ajudar a treinar?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:104
translate portuguese tammyspar1_f420071e:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do this."
    pc "Sim, vamos a isso."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:107
translate portuguese tammyspar1_7329cae6:

    # "We get into the ring and train hard for a couple of hours."
    "Entramos no ringue e treinamos intensamente durante umas duas horas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:108
translate portuguese tammyspar1_91f2a02c:

    # "She holds back on her punches and kicks, but man after a few hundred of them they really start to hurt."
    "Ela poupa os socos e pontapés, mas, caramba, depois de algumas centenas deles, começam mesmo a doer."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:109
translate portuguese tammyspar1_cc658c83:

    # "We practice all of the movements, holds, and attacks that she wants to focus on for the fight."
    "Praticamos todos os movimentos, chaves e ataques em que ela quer concentrar-se para a luta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:112
translate portuguese tammyspar1_3589480a:

    # "And by the end, we are lying in puddles of our own sweat on the mat."
    "E no final, estamos deitados em poças do nosso próprio suor no tapete."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:113
translate portuguese tammyspar1_5031ce49:

    # pc "My everything hurts."
    pc "Dói-me tudo."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:114
translate portuguese tammyspar1_65be1fb3:

    # tm "Good. That's how I want my opponent to feel."
    tm "Ótimo. É assim que quero que o meu adversário se sinta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:115
translate portuguese tammyspar1_209b5ba6:

    # pc "You feeling good about the fight now?"
    pc "Estás a sentir-te bem em relação à luta agora?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:116
translate portuguese tammyspar1_a82bf39b:

    # tm "Better for sure. I feel like I'm almost in the zone."
    tm "Melhor, com certeza. Sinto que estou quase no meu melhor."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:117
translate portuguese tammyspar1_3b41957d:

    # tm "One more sparring session should do it."
    tm "Mais uma sessão de sparring deve bastar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:118
translate portuguese tammyspar1_de22b3bd:

    # tm "You up for it?"
    tm "Estás a postos?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:119
translate portuguese tammyspar1_c4a56d2f:

    # pc "My heart is willing, but my body is bruised."
    pc "O meu coração está disposto, mas o meu corpo está cheio de contusões."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:120
translate portuguese tammyspar1_e5162b79:

    # tm "Aw, you'll be okay."
    tm "Ah, vais ficar bem."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:121
translate portuguese tammyspar1_45351dd0:

    # tm "Might be something good in it for you too."
    tm "Pode ser que haja algo de bom nisso para ti também."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:122
translate portuguese tammyspar1_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "Ah, sim?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:123
translate portuguese tammyspar1_3aaffb9d:

    # tm "After the fight, I could see some good things going your way."
    tm "Depois da luta, vejo algumas coisas boas a acontecerem para ti."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:124
translate portuguese tammyspar1_d93e675a:

    # tm "Assuming I win of course."
    tm "Partindo do princípio que eu ganho, claro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:125
translate portuguese tammyspar1_6d5412f5:

    # pc "You'll win. You're a great fighter."
    pc "Vais ganhar. És uma excelente lutadora."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:126
translate portuguese tammyspar1_ade4dc1d:

    # tm "Thanks."
    tm "Obrigada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:127
translate portuguese tammyspar1_7c0189e9:

    # tm "I'm going to go clean up. I'll see you next time."
    tm "Vou tomar banho. Até à próxima."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:128
translate portuguese tammyspar1_e08706c1:

    # pc "Alright. Bye, Tammy."
    pc "Tudo bem. Adeus, Tammy."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:131
translate portuguese tammyspar1_9ae56f74:

    # "She goes to the showers. I clean up too and then leave the gym for the day."
    "Ela vai para os chuveiros. Eu também me limpo e depois saio do ginásio por hoje."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:137
translate portuguese tammyspar1_cc85c375:

    # "Now I need to hurry and get to school."
    "Agora preciso de me apressar e ir para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:149
translate portuguese tammyspar2_6f0ed0c2:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. Ready to help me train?"
    tm "Ei, [pcname]. Pronto para me ajudar a treinar?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:150
translate portuguese tammyspar2_c640c08c:

    # pc "I'm still sore from last time, but sure."
    pc "Ainda estou dorido da última vez, mas claro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:152
translate portuguese tammyspar2_d4e6c2a5:

    # tm "Aw, look at you, toughing it out for me."
    tm "Olha só para ti, a aguentar tudo por mim."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:153
translate portuguese tammyspar2_48881b94:

    # pc "I want you to win this thing. Especially if I'm going to be in your corner."
    pc "Quero que ganhes isto. Especialmente se eu estiver no teu canto."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:154
translate portuguese tammyspar2_bfe1fd8b:

    # tm "Then let's get training. I want to win this thing too."
    tm "Então vamos treinar. Eu também quero ganhar isto."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:156
translate portuguese tammyspar2_374feca3:

    # "We go over everything one more time, working even harder than the previous sessions."
    "Revisamos tudo mais uma vez, a treinar ainda mais intensamente do que nas sessões anteriores."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:157
translate portuguese tammyspar2_20006225:

    # "By the end, Tammy is moving like a machine, every dodge and punch, every grappling movement, all just instinct and muscle memory."
    "No final, a Tammy está a mover-se como uma máquina, cada esquiva e cada soco, cada movimento de luta, tudo apenas instinto e memória muscular."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:159
translate portuguese tammyspar2_4e4c5a23:

    # "Until finally, we can't take any more and we collapse together onto the mat."
    "Até que, finalmente, não aguentamos mais e caímos juntas no tapete."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:160
translate portuguese tammyspar2_a068ca78:

    # tm "I feel really good about this fight now."
    tm "Agora sinto-me muito confiante em relação a esta luta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:161
translate portuguese tammyspar2_51b8a4f7:

    # tm "Thanks for all the training. You've been a huge help."
    tm "Obrigada por todo o treino. Foste uma grande ajuda."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:162
translate portuguese tammyspar2_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "Sempre à disposição."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:163
translate portuguese tammyspar2_60bd297a:

    # pc "Actually, I take that back. I'm going to need a little while to recuperate from this."
    pc "Na verdade, retiro o que disse. Vou precisar de algum tempo para recuperar disto."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:164
translate portuguese tammyspar2_310e49e5:

    # tm "Ha!"
    tm "Ha!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:165
translate portuguese tammyspar2_0fdae2e9:

    # tm "Well the fight is coming up."
    tm "Bem, a luta está a chegar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:166
translate portuguese tammyspar2_8f754bdf:

    # pc "I'll be there in your corner."
    pc "Estarei lá no teu canto."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:167
translate portuguese tammyspar2_29a4fcc0:

    # tm "Good. I want you to have a front-row seat to me kicking this chick's ass."
    tm "Ótimo. Quero que tenhas um lugar na primeira fila para me veres a dar uma coça a esta miúda."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:168
translate portuguese tammyspar2_a2038558:

    # pc "I wouldn't miss it."
    pc "Não ia perder isso por nada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:169
translate portuguese tammyspar2_e296303f:

    # tm "Thanks again, [pcname]. You're the best."
    tm "Mais uma vez obrigada, [pcname]. És o melhor."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:170
translate portuguese tammyspar2_4cac4a98:

    # tm "And I'll be sure to pay you back somehow after the fight."
    tm "E vou garantir que te retribua de alguma forma depois da luta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:171
translate portuguese tammyspar2_6dcf86da:

    # pc "Can't wait."
    pc "Mal posso esperar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:172
translate portuguese tammyspar2_65346d04:

    # tm "Alright, I'm going to head out."
    tm "Muito bem, vou dar uma volta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:173
translate portuguese tammyspar2_1523472a:

    # pc "Me too. See ya Tammy."
    pc "Eu também. Até logo, Tammy."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:174
translate portuguese tammyspar2_6471f1e5:

    # tm "Bye, [pcname]."
    tm "Adeus, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:176
translate portuguese tammyspar2_a23552f4:

    # "We get cleaned up and then leave the gym."
    "Arrumamo-nos e depois saímos do ginásio."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:177
translate portuguese tammyspar2_89763f7f:

    # "Tammy's fight is coming up this weekend. I can't wait to see her win this thing."
    "A luta da Tammy está a chegar este fim de semana. Mal posso esperar para a ver a ganhar isto."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy5.rpy:183
translate portuguese tammyspar2_cc85c375:

    # "Now I need to hurry and get to school."
    "Agora preciso de me apressar e ir para a escola."

